product.short_description:
Sure to become an everyday staple, the<b> Ampersand Patch Tote</b> from <b>CAMILLA AND MARC</b>&nbsp;effortlessly features a tanned leather patch, debossed with the brands <i>Ampersand</i>&nbsp;insignia. Made with organic cotton, it is the perfect minimal bag for all your on-the-go essentials.<br><br>
- Dimensions: H36cm x W32cm x D12cm<br>
- Organic cotton twill outer<br>- Leather handles and base<br>- Monogram embossed patch to front<br>- Snap-fastened fastening<br>- Inner zip pocket&nbsp;
